== 0.3 07/02/10

   * More callbacks in RubotoActivity
   * Toggle usable screen real estate
   * Copy IRB output to editor
   * Clear IRB output
   * HistoryEditText uses auto complete
   * Auto reload of scripts list
   * Craps script demo

== 0.2 06/16/10

   * RubotoActivity for creating UI and getting callbacks
   * New demo scripts
   * Shortcuts
   * New package name
   * JRuby 1.5.1

== 0.1 03/01/10

   * First official release to Android Marketplace
   * Issues #4, #6, #7

== 0.x 02/21/10

 Various improvements from Pascal Chatterjee
 (http://code.google.com/p/jruby-for-android) and Scott Moyer:

   * scripts can now be edited and saved to sd card
   * fix for issue #2 (rotating display is slow) (rscottm)
